                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14371537" author="msahyoun" created="Fri, 20 Mar 2015 16:06:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;looking at &lt;tt&gt;addSignature(PDSignature sigObject, SignatureInterface signatureInterface)&lt;/tt&gt; this calls &lt;tt&gt;addSignature(PDSignature sigObject, SignatureInterface signatureInterface, SignatureOptions options)&lt;/tt&gt; with a &lt;tt&gt;new SignatureOptions()&lt;/tt&gt; object. In there the default page number is set to &lt;tt&gt;1&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So I think we have to change the default page number in &lt;tt&gt;SignatureOptions()&lt;/tt&gt; too as &lt;tt&gt;catalog.getPages().get(startIndex)&lt;/tt&gt; is zero-based.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cbremaud&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cbremaud&quot;&gt;cbremaud&lt;/a&gt; would you have a small test case to validate the changes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14372595" author="jira-bot" created="Sat, 21 Mar 2015 08:29:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1668206 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=msahyoun&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;msahyoun&quot;&gt;msahyoun&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1668206&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1668206&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2719&quot; title=&quot;The addSignature() method always set the visual signature on the last page of the PDF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2719&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2719&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; don&apos;t set signature always at last page&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14375623" author="cbremaud" created="Mon, 23 Mar 2015 09:37:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It works, thank you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
